{"tid":795771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人以為自己大個就會唔怕醜","createTime":"2018-08-27T09:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T16:28:19.000Z","uid":6425,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c1b9b11e7a1b4ba6025fad7d66c2e50f0ff678","tid":795771,"uid":6425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"細個見啲大人好似好勁<br />\n同咩人都講到野<br />\n以為大個就會外向左<br />\n但到左自己做左「大人」<br />\n仲係咁怕醜同唔講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同啲大人相差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d14b5244774d8a8aa298a53a4941eef3cf0e66e","tid":795771,"uid":129660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"仲怕醜過以前<br />\n<br />\n依家直頭對住細路定大人都唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5738aed6f884a4fe3283d1608081f1b58aeedad5","tid":795771,"uid":160579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"我細個見到陌生人完全都唔敢講嘢<br />\n大個份人有自信咗好咗啲<br />\n但對住啲叻過自己嘅人都係唔敢出聲 驚獻醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709f0043213223e9962287000862dabe286474a3","tid":795771,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"成日比人話我靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5788ad023581d9d2655063117394d277ba6c4f55","tid":795771,"uid":6425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"709f0043213223e9962287000862dabe286474a3","tid":795771,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"成日比人話我靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"我都係平時唔點講野<br />\n有次同個同事做緊野，因為都幾忙，我就係咁講話咩好煩呀<br />\n之後佢就話 原來你咁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不